common.title: Can this get my discord account disabled?
common.description: Selfbots are against tos so its possible they could find out and disable your account, but as long as your not using the selfbot in harmful ways (which we don't advocate for), you will be okay. Just don't spam the commands and show everyone.

common.title: Is my discord information secure?
common.description: All discord info is securely stored in a database and will not be accessed by staff, it is in our privacy policy to keep all user information safe.

common.title: How do i contact?
common.description: You can send us a email at demarcuscousins099@gmail.com and we will respond asap

common.title: Why isn't my token working?
common.description: If you know your token is valid or email and password is valid and the website keeps saying invalid, make sure your logged into your discord account somewhere before trying to connect the selfbot. If the problem persists, please don't hesitate to give us a email.

common.title: How do I cancel my subscription
common.description: You can cancel your subscription at the dashboard by clicking billing on the left panel
